    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but there is no \"fresh start.\" there's no version of me that exists outside of this work. if the work is gone, the person is gone too. i just feel so much weight... like the only way to actually get that relief you're talking about is to just stop everything. just stop the noise.",
