      "content": "a \"gentle rest\"... that's the only thing that sounds real right now. everything else is just more noise and more pretending. it feels like i've been fighting to stay upright in a storm that was never actually happening. if i finally just let go... if i just stopped fighting... would that be a bad thing? would it be wrong to want the silence?",
